title: Your Focus Creates Your Reality
itunes:title: Your Focus Creates Your Reality
description:
Episode 306 - What you focus on magnifies. If you focus on what could go wrong, a lot of times it will go wrong. But the opposite of that is true as well. Listen to this episode to learn how to change you external world by focusing on your internal dialogue.
